Pre-Game Insights: England vs Pakistan T20I series will start tonight (May 22) in Leeds.
Both teams will look forward to gaining momentum in this series before the T20 World Cup 2024 in West Indies and USA.
Pakistan registered a 2-1 T20I series win against Ireland earlier this month.
Captain Jos Buttler will try to finalize his playing XI for T20 World Cup 2024 during this series.
